--- !u!114 &6458252332150589229
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 6458252332150589232}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 0
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '- Added the ability to set the region of the server to connect to.

    -
    Added language settings (English and Japanese are supported)

    - Added the
    ability to freely select the first player in a room match (selectable only by
    the room creator).

    - Added the ability to choose whether to confirm the
    selection of cards before it is completed.

    - Added a function to select
    the last selected deck by default.

    - Changed the font of the text on the
    home screen.

    - Changed "Card Kind" to "Card Type" on the deck edit screen.

    -
    Fixed a bug that caused cards in the trash to be backside up.

    - Fixed a
    bug that caused overflow when placing Digimon ACE under another Digimon or Tamer
    in Arresterdramon: Superior Mode (BT12-083).

    - Fixed a bug in which Takuya
    Kanbara''s (BT12-088) inherited effect could gain memory when Terriermon (BT3-046)
    was in the battle area.

    - Fixed a bug that the [All Turns] effect of Rust
    Tyrannomon ACE (P-113) did not activate during the opponent''s turn.

    - Fixed
    a bug that prevented the effect of Mirei Mikagura (BT11-094) from bringing up
    "Angewomon" or "LadyDevimon".

    - Fixed a bug that the effect of Yashamon
    cannot play Ryoma Mogami (BT12-097).

    - Fixed a bug that caused the game
    to freeze when using the [When Digivolving] effect of Sakuyamon: Maid Mode (BT10-041)
    or Taomon (BT10-039).

    - Fixed a bug that prevented Fusionize (BT11-105)
    from digivolving its own Digimon to Galacticmon (BT11-111).

    - Fixed a bug
    that Destromon (P-094)''s [On Play] [When Digivolving] effect could not target
    tamers.

    - Fixed a bug that caused the [When Digivolving] effect of Baihumon
    (BT9-069) to be triggered as [On Play].

    - Fixed a bug that caused MegaGargomon''s
    (EX2-029) [When Digivolving] effect to be triggered as [On Play].

    - Fixed
    a bug that caused Monzaemon''s (BT14-039) [On Play] effect to be triggered as
    [When Digivolving].

    - Fixed a bug in which MagnaAngemon''s (BT1-060) inherited
    effect was still applied on the opponent''s turn.

    - Fixed a bug that caused
    Zhuqiaomon''s (BT8-019) Security Attack to only gain +1 when multiple Digimon
    deleted at the same time.

    - Fixed a bug that the order of cards displayed
    when cards are placed on the deck by the effects of CatchMamemon(BT8-065), Mamemon(BT11-068),
    etc. is reversed.

    - Fixed a bug that after using Win Rate:60% (EX1-071),if
    you use [Main] effect of Takuya Kanbara (BT7-085) or Kouji Minamoto (BT7-087)
    and trash your hand, you cannot digivolution.

    - Fixed a bug that [Barrier]
    could only be used once per turn.

    - Fixed a bug that <Security Attack-1>
    was not applied by Etemon (BT11-041)''s [On Play] [When Digivolving] effect.

    -
    Fixed a bug that the "When a card in removed from yhour security stack" effect
    was not applied when using the  Omegamon X antibody (BT10-086)''s [When Digivolving][Whne
    Attacking]  effect.

    - Fixed a bug that when using the [When Digivolving][Whne
    Attacking] effect of Omegamon X Antibody (BT10-086), the animation of the digivolution
    card leaving the Digimon was displayed twice.

    - Fixed a bug that you can
    choose not to place card in security stack by Reinforce Memory Boost! (BT6-100).

    -
    Fixed a bug in Shoutmon X4 (BT10-009) [End of Attack] effect that only one card
    can be placed under the tamer instead of all of them.

    - Fixed a bug that
    prevented Mist Memory Boost!(BT8-108) from being found when searching for "Memory
    Boost!"

    - Fixed display of effects when cards in the field battle or delete.

    -
    Fixed a bug that prevented the [Main] effect from being activated when Odin''s
    Breath (BT13-106) was trashed from security by the effect of your card.

    -
    Fixed a bug that prevented the effect of Dr. Niseagumon (EX4-052) from being
    activated.

    - Fixed a bug that caused the game to freeze when a Digimon that
    digivolved from ZiegGreymon (BT5-017) attacked with an effect other than the
    [Blitz] effect.

    - Fixed a bug that the [Opponent''s Turn] effect of Baihumon
    ACE(EX5-053) is not activated when an opponent''s Digimon with Security Attack
    2 or more attacks to security and a Digimon with "Deva" was revealed on the second
    security check.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 83e4a8c28a636e04cb43dc01214a9a41, type: 2}
